
==================================================================

for DJGPP:

- environment variables that must be set:

DJGPP=c:\djgpp\djgpp.env
GRX20DRV=VESA gw 800 gh 600 nc 256
GRXFONT=c:\djgpp\fonts

- directory that must be in the path:

PATH=C:\DJGPP\BIN

==================================================================

- for coloring of nodes and lines: 		grid -C file

- to extract lines and single nodes from file: 	exgrd -Es file

==================================================================

Line types:

	1	external boundary line
	2	internal boundary line (island)
	4	internal fault line (not closed)

==================================================================

